{"tid":1906842,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎：法國2市長確診　成歐洲官員首例","createTime":"2020-03-02T07:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T16:31:45.000Z","uid":34899,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9e59cb3aeb483c7a3f0ea4f959463632398ae760","tid":1906842,"uid":34899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T07:59:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200302/bkn-20200302080606379-0302_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200302%2Fbkn-20200302080606379-0302_00912_001.html&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=63523db3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200302/bkn-20200302080606379-0302_00912_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎蔓延歐洲，法國周日（1日）新增30宗確診個案至130宗，包括瓦茲省及薩瓦省的2名市長，是歐洲首次有政府官員確診；德國同日一口氣增加了63宗病例至129宗。另外，法國羅浮宮的員工因憂心染病，最終投票通過停工，博物館周日全日關閉，暫未知幾時重開。<br />\n法國衞生總局局長薩洛蒙周日（1日）表示，該國新冠肺炎確診病例累積增至130宗，死亡人數維持在兩人，另外有116人仍留院治療，當中9人病情嚴重，12人已康復。薩洛蒙補充指，確診個案中有72宗與群眾聚集或互相傳染有關，其中35人在國外感染，23宗尚在調查中。<br />\n而在德國，當局同日公布當地確診新冠肺炎個案累計129宗，差不多是前一日早上66宗的2倍。確診個案遍及全國16個州的其中9個，其中有超過一半、即74名患者在北萊茵-威斯特法倫州。該州自從在上月15日舉行的嘉年華中，有一對夫婦確診之後，成為了疫情的熱點。"},{"pid":"1bc686ae14c089b2bd3b3a167a756d08dff510f2","tid":1906842,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:07:50.000Z","msg":"玩完"},{"pid":"7fc9fc9185e3497b143b1f7e781c1de7064c199a","tid":1906842,"uid":16676,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:10:33.000Z","msg":"黑死病 2020"},{"pid":"22484450eb82a7ef360bc74f348bf807a037c921","tid":1906842,"uid":249924,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:12:33.000Z","msg":"全世界多得支那 屌 咁耐以黎對呢個世界零貢獻 真係應該滅國"},{"pid":"ff93aa7334577a229bee22bf8f6397d132d1e180","tid":1906842,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:14:43.000Z","msg":"信世衛, 死全家"},{"pid":"69e4a207fc5fc2fa32ffc8e489d5903c59696970","tid":1906842,"uid":170285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:15:51.000Z","msg":"中國出來道歉未？"},{"pid":"b787daaab57e20f8fb6a7a042d5fa0c5672e51c8","tid":1906842,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:37:15.000Z","msg":"好明顯法國唔識讓領導先走"},{"pid":"6ec002e1b88279eb61cffcb998ab51c25572a054","tid":1906842,"uid":293677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2cgQW2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2cgQW2.png&h=d08f08ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1bc10856d9ee6b8cf3421e1d15063528bc30405","tid":1906842,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:28:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1889ea0b1d95efd0c12ccc7c4fe40471db62c5e7","tid":1906842,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:29:31.000Z","msg":"gg"},{"pid":"a44669752d07ecc1f2f1c471b77c1b8588f57d23","tid":1906842,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:31:45.000Z","msg":"投降國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}